title: Winners and Losers of the 2019 NFL draft
itunes:title: Winners and Losers of the 2019 NFL draft
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap the the 2019 NFL Draft that was filled with many surprises. Josh Rosen has been traded to the Dolphins (4:20) shortly after Kyler Murray was drafted first and the heroes also discuss how Joe Flacco will handle a new rookie QB drafted under him (24:29).
